clx <-function(fm, dfcw, cluster){
  library(sandwich)
  library(lmtest)
  M <- length(unique(cluster))
  N <- length(cluster)
  dfc <- (M/(M-1))*((N-1)/(N-fm$rank))
  u <- apply(estfun(fm),2,function(x) tapply(x, cluster, sum))
  vcovCL <- dfc*sandwich(fm, meat=crossprod(u)/N)*dfcw
  coeftest(fm, vcovCL) }
